# .gitignore — Magna Enso
# Governed public-repository exclusions. Evidence intended for Git is not ignored.
# NOTE: trace/evidence/** is intentionally NOT ignored — Light Curves are real, version-controlled evidence.

# --- OS / editor noise ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
.idea/
.vscode/

# --- Secrets / environment (defense-in-depth; none exist yet) ---
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.key
*.pem
secrets/

# --- Future runtime build artifacts (none exist in Sprint 1) ---
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.venv/
venv/
node_modules/
dist/
build/
*.log

# --- Local-only review memory & scratch (defensive) ---
# ChatGPTReview/ is a SIBLING of this repo and is naturally excluded when the repo
# root is magna-enso/. These entries are belt-and-suspenders in case anything is ever
# created or symlinked inside the repo by mistake.
ChatGPTReview/
**/ChatGPTReview/
*scratch*/
*hermes-audit*/

# --- Local validation and browser artifacts ---
.gitleaks-report*.json
playwright-report/
test-results/
artifacts/
coverage/
